		<div class="productHeaderText">
			<h2>DTerm</h2>
      <h4>A command line anywhere and everywhere</h4>
      <p>Command line work isn't a separate task that should live on its ownâ€”it's an integrated part of your natural workflow. DTerm provides a context-sensitive command line that makes it fast and easy to run commands on the files you're working with and then use the results of those commands.</p>
			<div class="buttonGroup">
      <div class="downloadHover">	
				<a href="http://files.decimus.net/DTerm/DTerm.zip" class="downloadButton inline"><span>Download DTerm</span></a>
